Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇好诱人太完美了 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前已经拍过很多作品了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是采访的内容不是很多吧？--嗯不多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常都是一开拍就直接打炮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就换种方式问一些真实内容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜头太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 来点和正常采访不同的 那么……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边摸边采访怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个问题 什么地方最敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸大腿 是大腿内侧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内侧更敏感一些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得非常有性欲想做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就反复地来回摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你知道怎么做吗？ --我懂的 我非常有经验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很软啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富有弹性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续提问了 对你来说 大鸡巴是如同什么样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的存在？--嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有的话 就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的 我无法理解 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸吗？这次来刺激刺激你 用这个来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有就活不下去是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒对你来说就是生活的必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽 --已经开始爽了哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很快乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面来回挑逗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个往上提一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次体验鸡巴是什么时候？ --15岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 好像是高一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不知道这个猥琐男叫什么床）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多久自慰一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都自慰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上起来做一次 晚上睡前做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和做爱不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能哪里有人偷看到 很刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我男友用牙齿咬的感觉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙齿咬 真变态？呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他做爱不咋滴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人舔你 感觉不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 直接碰到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看你下面 让我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩你的下面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 把腿张开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 太难为情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难为情？没事的 让我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想舔啊 很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看里面 帮我掰开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行 已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么湿滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了 高潮高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太下流了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的屄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个更长一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ --鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴？鸡巴怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要鸡巴 --想要鸡巴是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有五个鸡巴 够你爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要精液
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个给她精液 明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你想要 --我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射到哪里？ --全部射到我嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这模样 大家都勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全给你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的话就别做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精液还是想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精液随时都可以给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 下一个来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要吗？ --还想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身好热
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好浓稠 --快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不会断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了 最后一发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调强一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后再高潮一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了 --给我高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒的内射
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.78,0:44:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
